PUBLIC DOMAIN DEDICATION

The original God of Thunder source code was released to the public domain by
Ron Davis on 2020-03-27.

The native port code (raylib platform layer, unified game engine, launcher,
extras menu, AdLib emulation bridge, and build system) is also released to the
public domain. You may use it for any purpose without restriction.

GAME ASSETS

The game graphics are copyright their original creators and may not be used in
commercial projects. The music and sound effects are by Roy Davis and are
public domain; attribution to "Roy Davis" is appreciated.

THIRD-PARTY CODE

The ymfm OPL emulation library (third_party/ymfm/) is copyright its authors
and is licensed under the BSD 3-Clause License. See third_party/ymfm/LICENSE
for details.

raylib is fetched at build time and is licensed under the zlib/libpng License.
